#

Tofu and Spinach Scramble

20 min
$5
200 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

Soy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianVeganGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Breakfast

Tags:

BreakfastQuickHealthy

Description

A quick, protein-packed scramble with tofu and fresh spinach, perfect for a nutritious breakfast or lunch!

Ingredients

  • firm tofu: 1 block (14 oz)
  • fresh spinach: 2 cups
  • olive oil: 1 tablespoon
  • turmeric: 1/2 teaspoon
  • garlic powder: 1/2 teaspoon
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • optional: nutritional yeast: 2 tablespoons
